:markdown
  An interface implemented by all Angular type decorators, which allows them to be used as ES7
  decorators as well as
  Angular DSL syntax.
  
  DSL syntax:
  
  ```
  var MyClass = ng
    .Component({...})
    .View({...})
    .Class({...});
  ```
  
  ES7 syntax:
  
  ```
  @ng.Component({...})
  @ng.View({...})
  class MyClass {...}
  ```
  
  
